content:
Use Context Definitions as Mapping Data Source

Map a context definition to other context definitions to retrieve data from a definition. Previously, you selected from Salesforce objects to fetch data from standard objects.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Professional, Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions for Industries clouds where Context Service is enabled.

How: On the Context Definition Objects tab, select the definition that you want to map, and click Done.
title: Use Context Definitions as Mapping Data Source in Salesforce
